Bharat Petroleum Said to Buy Qua Iboe Crude From Exxon Mobil

-- B y   S h e r r y   S u   a n d   P r a t i s h   N a r a y a n a n
-- 
2011-07-08T08:19:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/bharat-petroleum-said-to-buy-qua-iboe-crude-from-exxon-mobil.html
Bharat Petroleum Corp. bought about 1
million barrels of Nigerian Qua Iboe crude for loading in August
from  Exxon Mobil Corp. (XOM) , said three people who declined to be
identified because they aren’t authorized to speak to the media.  In May, Bharat Petroleum,  India ’s second-largest state-run
oil refiner, bought 1 million barrels of Angolan Nemba crude for
July from Total SA through a spot tender.  Details of the purchase are as follows:  To contact the reporters on this story:
